{"tid":1518852,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（核彈級文宣）美國國歌廣東話版歌詞","createTime":"2019-08-30T11:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T11:38:48.000Z","uid":292710,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1653b641af7ba1fa5a53ef2b4f7c492a0d4745cc","tid":1518852,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:20:04.000Z","msg":"小弟岩岩寫左首美國國歌歌詞，廣東話版。<br />\n希望大家聽日會唱<br />\n利申：反陳雲，城邦共諜早日收皮。<br />\nCredit by：石室遺錄<br />\n<br />\n聽自由號角聲<br />\n星條旗漸生輝<br />\n人情心中閃照<br />\n誰在今天已無言<br />\n試問何日覺醒<br />\n拋開往時舊怨<br />\n聯邦合眾一心<br />\n能令江山光復<br />\n但願義勇蒼生<br />\n莫忘辛亥血淚<br />\n終於起革命<br />\n革去多年暴政<br />\n在獅子山上 啊我們走出了新路<br />\n誰仍在 而在我心<br />\n是勇者的新家"},{"pid":"ec9c14048136d22e61aa93f1c41f51271ad1253e","tid":1518852,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:20:23.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831無大台 自行選地點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=32dc60cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=5bdc3561\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouope